Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:16.52,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've bonded with a new friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,which has allowed you to obtain the Priestess Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The disaster looming in your future is claiming human lives as it draws ever closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You already possess the power to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When you truly need us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the door will open, and we shall offer you our assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2C4CB3&}I'm hot! I'm on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do with my melting hot body?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to thrust...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,deeper in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible! We actually went inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. This is Yukiko's first time coming here on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't know where Tatsumi Kanji is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can smell that someone's here, but I can't figure out where.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because I've got so much on my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like where did I come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you? Your head's totally empty inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what can we do? Our hands are tied if Teddie can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So like, wanna call it quits this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha— Narukami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could find him if you gave me a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got anything with his scent on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but he hasn't been home since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been dangerous out lately, so I notified the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He always leaves without saying a word, but this is the first time he hasn't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's surprising. I figured he'd usually be out at night fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll admit he can be a little rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A while ago, he got into a fight with some biker kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean how he beat up an entire biker gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was partially my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep because of their loud bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That made him angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So he beat up a biker gang for his mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about an aggressive momma's boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, is that guy in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Um, see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed Sana's cell phone strap with a doll on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but I lost the doll and couldn't find it anywhere.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\t(\blur4.5)}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF\t(\blur4.5)}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down! There's no use crying over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make an exact copy, but I could make something like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Just apologize when you give it to her and ask for her forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He even made one for me to match Sana's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Tatsumi Kanji made that strap from scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,May I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! It doesn't even look handmade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what to think of Kanji making something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! It defies my image of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has their thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sana forgave me because of him, so I wanted to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, could I ask you for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,His scent should be on it if he made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Didn't we see him yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? Tatsumi has gone into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, what did you and Kanji talk about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair enough. I'll tell you upfront since you seem to be in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was ask him about his recent activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It was just small talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I think about it, he was acting a little peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Peculiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And I bluntly told him as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "You're weird."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That made the color drain from his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's surprising. He doesn't seem like the type to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't judge a book by its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be struggling with some sort of complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff, sniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This bear acts like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've got Kanji's scent down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to pick up the trail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fail me now, nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff! Sniff, sniff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think I found something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like our target! Is this it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Kanji here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it me, or is the fog here different?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My glasses are fogging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it's hot in here! It's just like a—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mere, pussycat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Such well-defined pecs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be scared, so just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec! I don't wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teddie, is Kanji really in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The nose knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're really going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I seriously don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way too risky! There's no turning back once we're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I might lose something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! We're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Lemme go! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not ready to give up my pure body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I should just leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's hot. This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna leave so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka and Amagi can charge in while you and I go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell it is! You're not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to save Kanji, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not as bad as I thought, so we gotta save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my. Thank you for your attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kanji!{i didn't know kanji meant gay...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! We're gonna snap if we don't get this over with quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming at you live from the Suspicious Tropical Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The hot steam is making my heart go wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Not you too, Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. He was pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since everyone's burning up, let's move on to the next segment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad... in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just like it was with Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Mine was nothing like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do the people who get thrown in here create these images?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine was like this? No, that can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, in my hunt for more love,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall thrust...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,deeper in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how it was with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That... That...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up, Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use your fire spells when it's already this hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too damn hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm freezing. How about a little moderation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see what Hanamura was getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go crazy if we stay here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time he creeps me out, he's toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, what is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone there?! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsumi Kanji's a violent delinquent and a bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He trashed a biker gang and became their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks he's "King of the Mountain"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap! I never became their boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the one stealing kids' money at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not! Don't assume it was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly Tatsumi Kanji did it. He's that kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you make that shit up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out so I can kill ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you put on the scary delinquent act.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cut the crap"? You're such a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji, the strong and scary delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you want to be seen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in here, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but keep your cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, no one should lose their temper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we need to rescue Kanji. Then, we gotta save Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie, those two objectives were the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that was intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Amagi, I seriously don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you opening the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we really have to? I bet we're in for an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just picture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What should we do, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is when you guys take the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on! I said, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! You're so gentle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simply sublime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha— You guys?! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We, uh, came...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you sound so unmotivated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you interfere! Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Is this supposed to slow us down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! It's slimy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, got a video camera handy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think— Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you drop the charade?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with just saying what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm what you really want, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't listen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirai— Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I'll help— Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how I hate girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They look at me and say, "You like to sew? What a queer!" or "Painting is so not you."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk, if you don't shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"But you're a man! Why don't you act like a guy?! Why aren't you manly?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to be manly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't scared of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Men are much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd never say those awful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I vastly prefer men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you're me, and I'm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't say it, Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way in hell that you're me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me, and there's no denying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Shadow... The true self...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, my, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough shit outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be honest with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll get rid of anyone who gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this is how Kanji truly feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't how he feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His emotions are just going haywire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come on, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teddie! What's the big deal? We've got some real weirdos here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be a part of Kanji's Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what a stud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Cha—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just eat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster! He broke their spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! The guys are down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. They aren't interested in us, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Such vulgar red!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't any trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound lovely! It's making my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's time for one last hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,850)}It's time for you to awaken your wild card's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They merged together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't dislike this! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"But you're a man! Why don't act like a guy! You aren't you manly?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it even though I'm a dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cu—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It's cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's super-duper cute! I love anything cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I love cutesy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He defeated his own Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it made me happy when you called it cute and accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He... He's coming back for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You must really find him unbearable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't someone, anyone, accept me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, the mere thought that you've been inside me is disgraceful.{gay undertones}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't about men or women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just scared shitless of getting rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a total pansy who tries to make everyone hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me, and I'm you, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kanji's Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty masculine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, anyone would be surprised if they found out you made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop it! I'm over that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you're being so polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you guys are my seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:22:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, who was the jackass that threw me into the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we're trying to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're searching for the culprit? Can I help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta pay him back ten times over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For real? That'd be great! You'd be a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Is that okay, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Kanji Tatsumi, will risk my life for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi was telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that you were hanging out around Tatsumi Textiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend took me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't getting into any funny business, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.37,0:23:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're just talking.
